Mr Chen written several articles for the New Express alleging financial irregularities at a construction-equipment company called Zoomlion.
After he was detained, his newspaper published two one-page appeals for his release, saying it supported his journalism.
Mais M. Chen est alors apparu à la télévision d'État admettant qu'il avait publié de fausses histoires pour de l'argent.
